            <h1>OUR MISSION</h1>
            <p>There are 224.3 million people who are undernourished in India. Despite sufficient food production and tremendous economic growth, we are yet to address the challenge of eliminating hunger in India.</p>
            <p>We aim to build a strong and efficient network of FoodBanks with banquet halls.The goal of the network is to provide food to the food insecure and help transform lives.</p>
