              <h5 class="card-title">PROBLEM</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Nearly more than half of the world, goes to sleep on a empty stomach, where on the other side our store houses are overflowing with food. The shelf life of food products are very less and they expire very soon. Food shortage is a pressing global issue that continues to affect millions of people worldwide, posing significant challenges to food security and livelihoods. Additionally, shifting weather patterns alter the suitability of certain regions for farming, further compromising food production. </p>
